Texts.Chs: 联盟故事线 - 开始讯息
大使！你还好吗？自从我知道了地球和大地守护团发生的事情后，我一直在试图联系你...
Texts.Eng: Ambassador! Are you alright? I've been trying to contact you ever since I learned of what happened to Earth and the Protectorate...

Texts.Chs: 现在，我希望你们尽一切努力找出袭击大地守护团的幕后黑手。我们的首要任务是防止这种悲剧发生在更多的行星上。
Texts.Eng: For now, I want you to do all you can to figure out who or what was behind the attack on the Protectorate. Our first priority is to prevent this tragedy from happening to any more planets.

Texts.Chs: 祝你好运，大使。一旦我有一个新的任务为你准备好了我会再次联系你。
Texts.Eng: Good luck, ambassador. I will contact you again once I have a new assignment ready for you.

Texts.Chs: 我将很快与其他联盟领导人会面，讨论这些最近的事件，我们将决定你的下一个任务应该是什么。
Texts.Eng: I will meet with the other Alliance leaders soon to discuss these recent events, and we will figure out what your next assignment should be.

Texts.Chs: 很高兴看到你安然无恙地逃离了这场混乱。现在我们比以往任何时候都需要你这样的良才。
Texts.Eng: It is good to see you have escaped the chaos alive and well. Now more than ever, we need good people like you.

Texts.Chs: 这个任务是对联盟故事情节的介绍。你不应该在你的日志中看到这个。
Texts.Eng: This quest serves as an introduction to the Alliance storyline. You shouldn't be able to see this in your log.
